CHANGES TO THIRD-PARTY CODE

This project uses Pingora as a dependency via Cargo (crates.io v0.8.0).
No modifications have been made to the Pingora source code. Pingora is
used as-is through its public API.

The yaml_serde crate (formerly serde_yaml) is used via Cargo package
rename: serde_yaml = { package = "yaml_serde", version = "0.10" }.
No modifications to the source.
